short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A dark mode for the online LaTeX editor Overleaf.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension inverts colours in the editor, PDF viewer, and modals, and adds a dark background to most content panes. It may be toggled by clicking on the icon.
